    "description": "猛鬼大厦的前作现在搬到STEAM上来啦﹗<br><br>茶餐厅服务生&quot;阿仁&quot;对一个点外卖女生一见锺情，两人透过每天的送餐时间增长感情。在阿仁以为自己桃花运终于到来时，心仪的女生却突然失踪，更使阿仁陷入了万劫不復的深渊。究竟阿仁能否逃出生天，背后暗藏着的吓人又是甚么？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/f0dfefce43cba7625d6d730762797c38.poster.avif?t=1745924125\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/f0dfefce43cba7625d6d730762797c38.webm?t=1745924125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/f0dfefce43cba7625d6d730762797c38.mp4?t=1745924125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏特色：<br>-优质的剧情、真实度高的场景、配以悬疑的解谜，《都市传说 外卖》能让你体验到一款注重剧情故事的恐怖游戏。<br>-这款游戏未必是最出色的恐怖游戏，什至比起国产其他作品也许更是处处流露着廉价与简陋，但在游戏上我们却好努力地让各位玩家享受一款如同看戏般的感受，并且能细味故事中的情节与人物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/cd3610decb7c0af4110a2c90ec20cc19.poster.avif?t=1745924125\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/cd3610decb7c0af4110a2c90ec20cc19.webm?t=1745924125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/cd3610decb7c0af4110a2c90ec20cc19.mp4?t=1745924125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>全剧情粤语配音：<br>游戏所有剧情皆有粤语配音，能让玩家更能体验到从前港产电影特有的风貌及氛围，希望你体会到此游戏的特色及我们的诚意。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/5ce875c676b5aefe39b8fa43eacb6b36.poster.avif?t=1745924125\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/5ce875c676b5aefe39b8fa43eacb6b36.webm?t=1745924125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/5ce875c676b5aefe39b8fa43eacb6b36.mp4?t=1745924125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>多种分支及结局：<br>作为一款完整的剧情游戏，你的每一个选择都会影响故事的进展和最终结局。游戏中设有各种成就等待解锁，并且如以往一样拥有多于八个结局及数十个成就让你能多次重玩中找到惊喜及乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/76c9f02415e0eadfe612d5405c1a97d3.poster.avif?t=1745924125\" width=600 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/76c9f02415e0eadfe612d5405c1a97d3.webm?t=1745924125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3164860/extras/76c9f02415e0eadfe612d5405c1a97d3.mp4?t=1745924125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>欢迎加入我们的群组讨论游戏的内容及收到最新的G社游戏资讯。<br>QQ：820643985",
